Archana Karthick Couture for Pooja & Rhevanth, from Chennai, India
.
.
.
"Archana & Karthik were nothing short of GENIUS! From the first conversation, they understood our vision, even when we couldn’t fully articulate it ourselves. They took our Pinterest boards as a starting point and elevated the designs into something superrr special.

Every fitting felt like unwrapping a surprise—better than we could’ve ever dreamed! 😍 But what made the experience even more special was their vibe! Working with them felt like hanging out with friends who just get you. They weren’t just our designers—they became our friends, offering advice, sharing laughs, and making every meeting feel relaxed and fun. By the end of it, we didn’t just walk away with gorgeous outfits but with a beautiful new friendship. ☺️☺️

If you’re looking for designers who are creative, professional, and genuinely amazing people to work with, they’re the ones! 🥰"
- Pooja (Google Review)
.
.
.
"We were introduced to Archana Karthik through their reels on Instagram. Firstly They are one of the sweetest designers we have come across and they have mastered their skills to the tee. They brought into reality whatever we as a couple visualised, in-fact with improvisation that stole the show. Their knowledge is impeccable and they are truly the go to choice for ur Big day."
- Rhevanth (Google Review)
.
.
.
The Sangeet (Feb'24)
.
.
.
Out of the entire trousseau, the outfits for this occasion were the ones that challenged us creatively and morally. You'll see why, creatively, but morally because these two geniuses (listerally) had planned for us to design in secret. And it had to be kept an absolute secret till the day they saw each other for the Sangeet. The trials were like clandestine meetings with a lookout person kept at the entrance just in case the better half walked in unannounced. It was a complete roller coaster of joy, suspense and intrigue. We loved, admired and still can't get over these pieces.
.
.
